  "Send me... Send me someplace where I can be someone else. Let me forget all this and start over!"
  And then I fell. Coming down, I saw the tops of trees, it had to be a long way. Hit the ground, hit hard on my right leg so I could lose some momentum rolling. My forehead burned with a gash, but I survived the fall from...
  From the sky? I looked up and around; I was standing on god fucking dammit! I rolled on the ground, grabbing my snapped right leg. I was rolling around on a lonely field under an empty blue sky. What did I fall from? Who was I just shouting at?
  Aw, crap. And who am I? Isn't that just the clich√©?
